[HAS TO BE UPDATED TO GERBY]

For a new chapter:

1) Create tex file 

2) ./tex/Makefile:

LIJST = [..] filename

3) Same on /tex/tags/Makefile

4) ./tex/chapters.tex:

\item \hyperref[newchapter-section-phantom]{New Chapter}

5) ./tex/preamble.tex:

\externaldocument[newchapter-]{newchapter}

6) ./tex/tags/tags:

Create tags such as:

0150,newchapter-section-phantom
0151,newchapter-section-overview

7) Add parts, accordingly, in ./index.php

